&= \frac{1}{2}\left(1-\left(\frac{1}{216}\right)^{2} \times 216\right)\\
&= \frac{1}{2}\left(1-\frac{1}{216}\right)\\
&= \frac{1}{2} \times \frac{215}{216}\\
&= \boxed{\frac{215}{432}}.
\end{align*}
